						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1447 (1525 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Fragmentary. Records gift of land by Vasavappa-nāyakkar, son of Tippaya-nāyakkar for offerings on the occasions of the gods procession on <hi rend="italic">Nambirāṉ</hi> (horse). The details of the date viz., <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1447, Pārthiva, Kaṉṉi śu. 10, Tuesday (Śravaṇa)</hi> regularly correspond to <hi rend="bold">1525 A.D., September 26 Tuesday, ·38, ·19.</hi></p>						

